      The beam shot back at  Magnus. The try had back fired. All the remaing goodness had been takeing out. And put into Magnus. 
     The Oracal came out in a vision. "Now your mission is complete." 
    Magnus grew. He bacame very primish. His truck mode was blushish white. Now he was ready to return to his training. And stop Dark Prime and Magmatron.

<P>     The Oracal came out in a vision. "Now your mission is complete." 
<P>    Magnus grew. He bacame very primish. His truck mode was blushish white. Now he was ready to return to his training. And stop Dark Prime and Magmatron.
